Product Id: Renewable Fuels Except Fuel Ethanol include biodiesel fuel (FAME), renewable diesel fuel (HDRD/HVO) and other renewable fuels.
Renewable Fuel Plant Co-Products Except Distillers Grains include industrial ethanol (food grade), distillers corn oil, glycerol/glycerine and other co-products.
Inventories of fuel stored for future use. Stocks are reported as of the last day of the month.
Beginning stocks are quantities held on the first day of the reporting month (start of day).
Cereal grains include wheat, corn, rye, barley, oats, and triticale.
Vegetable oils include canola oil, soya oil and other vegetable oils.
Other renewable plant feedstocks include agricultural biomass residues, forestry biomass residues, municipal solid waste, animals fats, other biomass residue feedstocks, used cooking oil, methanol.
